message: Failed at least one business validation rules

errors.description: [IRASC5-012]-An Invoice MUST have an Invoice currency code (IBT-005).
[IRASC5-013]-The Invoice currency code (IBT-005) MUST be coded using ISO code list 4217 alpha-3.

[IRASC5-014]-An Invoice MUST have an Accounting currency code (IBT-006) with value 'SGD', if the Invoice currency code (IBT-005) is not 'SGD'. Otherwise, the Accounting currency code (IBT-006) MUST NOT be provided.

[IRASC5-015]-If the Invoice currency code (IBT-005) is not 'SGD', the Invoice MUST have exactly one Additional Supporting Document as follows: Document type code (BT-SG-001) MUST be 'sgdtotal-excl-gst', Supporting document description MUST be provided, Invoiced object identifier MUST be 'SGD'.

[IRASC5-016]-If the Invoice currency code (IBT-005) is not 'SGD', the Invoice MUST have exactly one Additional Supporting Document as follows: Document type code (BT-SG-002) MUST be 'sgdtotal-incl-gst', Supporting document description MUST be provided, Invoiced object identifier MUST be 'SGD'.
[IRASC5-035]-An Invoice MUST have an Invoice total GST amount (IBT-110).
